 Sabrina Carpenter 的“Espresso”连续一个月排名第一https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenters-espresso-spends-full-month-at-number-one-3759495?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sabrina-carpenters-espresso-spends-full-月度第一Max PilleySat, 25 May 2024 16:15:40 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3759495 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌击败了 Billie Eilish 的《LUNCH》，登上了第二名的位置</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenters-espresso-spends-full-month-at-number-one-3759495">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 的《Espresso》 连续一个月占据第一名的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/sabrina_carpenter_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter</a> ) 的热门单曲《Espresso》连续一个月位居英国单曲榜榜首。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="193" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/espresso-sabrina-carpenter-spotify-streaming-3757741"><b>为什么 Sabrina Carpenter 的“Espresso”会接管 Spotify 算法？</b></a></li></ul><p>周五（5 月 24 日），这首歌被宣布连续第四周排名第一，阻止了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>的挑战，后者的歌曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilishs-feel-good-video-for-lunch-3757399">LUNCH</a> ”只能获得第二名。</p><p> “Espresso”连续四周的霸主地位与今年早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯</a>的“Texas Hold &#39;Em”不相上下，尽管<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-kahan">诺亚·卡汉</a>的“Stick Season”在一月和二月总共占据了七周的冠军位置。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sabrina Carpenter - 浓缩咖啡（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/eVli-tstM5E?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这首歌于上个月发布，是 Carpenter 2022 年热门专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-deluxe-edition-of-emails-i-cant-send-3412115">《Emails I Can&#39;t Send》</a>以及最近单曲《Nonsense》和《Feather》的后续歌曲。</p><p>这位歌手去年还推出了一张圣诞 EP，并与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)</a>一起上路，加入这位流行偶像的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-reflects-on-eras-tour-with-taylor-swift-what-a-whirlwind-3608849">行列，为她最近在美国和亚洲举行的“Eras”巡演提供支持</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-explains-meaning-behind-espresso-lyrics-3757350">卡彭特最近公开了她创作这首歌时的心态</a>。 “整首歌都充满了个性，这一点真的很令人兴奋，因为那些与人群一起现场演唱真的非常非常有趣，”她解释道。</p><p> “我认为，当人们不了解我的音乐或我是谁或任何其他东西时，他们可以只听一首歌，然后带着更好的理解我的幽默感离开。”</p><p>她接着说，这首歌是试图捕捉自信的时刻。 “这是我一生中的一次，我当时觉得自己很糟糕。我认为你并不总是有这种感觉，所以你必须捕捉那些你所做的时刻，因为这就是你找到那些小[宝石]的方式，”她说。</p><p> “对我来说，把它等同于咖啡因，这种成瘾真的很有趣，而且我确实有咖啡因成瘾。所以这对我来说真的是一个完整的循环。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenter-perform-espresso-and-more-on-snl-debut-3757523">卡彭特最近在<i>《周六夜现场》</i>中表演了这首歌</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-reacts-as-adele-hails-espresso-as-my-jam-3757899">阿黛尔则在拉斯维加斯的一场演出中将其誉为“我的即兴表演”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenters-espresso-spends-full-month-at-number-one-3759495">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 的《Espresso》 连续一个月占据第一名的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
